{"tid":376228,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【碎股市價沽】月供股票唔驚跌市　有銀行免3年手續費搶客","createTime":"2017-08-26T22:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T17:10:36.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"797a71b6f0c134752390bdf0ec76e25fa76a5125","tid":376228,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T22:55:15.000Z","msg":"眼見港股有起色，但大型藍籌入場費高，等到儲夠本錢又或錯失入貨時機。若然透過月供股票計畫，則可小本買貨積少成多，同時亦可收取股息，並利用「平均成本法」減低高位「接火棒」風險。本報比較銀行及證券行月供股票優惠，尤以南洋商業銀行最划算，免三年大部分收費，而且可以正股市價沽碎股。<br />\n<br />\n月供股票即每月以固定金額、持續於指定日子購入指定股票。由於每月投資額相同，故股價低殘時可買入較多股數，股價高時則買入較少股數，長遠「拉勻」每股成本。<br />\n<br />\n月供股票的主要收費為手續費，銀行一般會收取供款額的0.25%，當中已包括證券交易的佣金、印花稅、交易徵費及交易處理費。目前以南商的新優惠最抵，開戶後三年，每月可豁免最多50元手續費，加上本身已不收取存倉費、代收股息費等雜費，故只要每月供款額不超過2萬元，基本上三年買入收費全免（詳見比較表）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，並非所有股票都可以月供，而且月供股票的最大不便之處在於出現碎股，若「湊」不夠一手，則需以低於正股市價的碎股價沽予銀行。以股票數目計，南商、中銀香港、滙豐提供較多選擇，達120隻以上，覆蓋主要恒指成份股。若散戶鍾情中資股，南商及中銀香港的選擇更多，亦可月供人民幣計價的A股ETF，而且碎股可以正股市價沽出，屬市面上少有。<br />\n<br />\n至於沽出佣金方面，大部分銀行均收取成交額的0.25%，證券行收費就相對吸引，致富的沽出佣金僅收取0.0675%，每隻股票最低收40元，較銀行便宜一半有多。此外，證券行的月供股票選擇亦較廣，致富有超過200隻股票選擇，若客戶有特定股票要求，該行亦會按情況考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳洛嘉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170826/large/1503757167_aba9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170826%2Flarge%2F1503757167_aba9.gif&h=8a047c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57132751&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57132751%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170827&d=Z6mWvjkh4U%2FzXuqpUJjLFAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=4fb39e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57132751%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170827&h=285d52c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57132751&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170827</a>"},{"pid":"790191aedaffc28288e899b52488c7f73b1eb720","tid":376228,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d107b2f0de6c7b9f6124ccb7bc1f9267e6da3843","tid":376228,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"中銀供半年退反錢比你<br />\n但好似一次"},{"pid":"add68af1461ae9d6ab9e6b1d60d89df0ffaa489b","tid":376228,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:42:49.000Z","msg":"南洋又出返三年免佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f10d47af9a3d6ce677723df212ac051a1cb134","tid":376228,"uid":33065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中銀供半年退反錢比你<br />\n但好似一次</blockquote><br />\n有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf7d2d851afa8f4fca25641ccea37ed8cdb319b","tid":376228,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中銀供半年退反錢比你<br />\n但好似一次</blockquote><br />\n有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n優惠黎, 新客先有"},{"pid":"c7f8bc051efae9cc20df5e7b612456578db9b0f3","tid":376228,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:06:17.000Z","msg":"其實美股有冇月供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78319a87cca76911adba222aae78d7548e53851","tid":376228,"uid":10680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac0d483812d78938917595ce37cbb29578c478f","tid":376228,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply